title: Yuki Ogaki
text:
is a Japanese <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="Nagoya%20Grampus">Nagoya Grampus</a>.
Playing career.
Ogaki was born in <a href="Osaka%20Prefecture">Osaka Prefecture</a> on February 28, 2000. After graduating from high school, he joined <a href="J1%20League">J1 League</a> club <a href="Nagoya%20Grampus">Nagoya Grampus</a> in 2018.
